sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant AI
    participant ContextHook as UserPromptSubmit Hook
    participant Command as /arckit.{type}
    participant Template as Template System
    participant Quality as Quality Checklist
    participant Write as Write Tool
    
    User->>AI: /arckit.devops or /arckit.mlops or /arckit.finops
    AI->>ContextHook: Trigger
    ContextHook->>ContextHook: Scan projects/
    ContextHook->>ContextHook: List REQ, PRIN, DIAG, DATA
    ContextHook->>ContextHook: List external/ docs
    ContextHook-->>AI: Inject project inventory
    
    AI->>Command: Execute with context
    
    Command->>Command: Phase 1: Read artifacts<br/>(REQ, PRIN, DIAG, DATA, external/)
    Command->>Command: Phase 2: Analysis<br/>(Extract NFRs, map architecture)
    
    Command->>Template: Check templates-custom/{type}-template.md
    Template-->>Command: Custom or fallback to default
    
    Command->>Command: Phase 3: Generate strategy<br/>(15+ sections, traceability matrix)
    
    Command->>Quality: Validate
    Quality->>Quality: Common checks
    Quality->>Quality: Practice-specific checks
    Quality-->>Command: Pass/Fail + corrections
    
    Command->>Write: Phase 5: Write output<br/>ARC-{PID}-{TYPE}-v{VERSION}.md
    Write-->>Command: File written
    
    Command-->>User: Summary only<br/>(not full 1000+ line document)
